    "Regular exercise helps me maintain my overall health and well-being, and it helps me manage my heart failure and rheumatoid arthritis symptoms.",
    "It gives me more energy, better sleep, and a more positive outlook on life.",
    "It also helps me stay connected with my community and stay active.",
    "Physical activity also has many benefits for mental health, it helps me to clear my mind and feel better about myself.",
